Type: Package
Package: sGBJ
Title: sGBJ: survival extension of the Generalized Berk-Jones Test for Set-Based Inference in Genomics studies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Laura Villain, Thomas Ferte, Boris Hejblum
Maintainer: Laura Villain <laura.villain@gmail.com>
Description: This packages implements an extension of the GBJ statistic for
    survival data. It computes the sGBJ statistic and its p-value for testing 
    the association between a gene set and a time-to-event outcome with possible 
    adjustment on additional covariates.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    GBJ,
    stats,
    survival
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
